.DT
add_philosophy
Disk World creator help
add_philosophy

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_philosophy -  This method adds a philosphy into the current list of philosphies.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_philosophy(string name,
string type,
int bonus,
string needed,
string effect)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the philosophy
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of the philosophy
%^BOLD%^bonus%^RESET%^ - the bonus of the philosophy
%^BOLD%^needed%^RESET%^ - the string describing what you need
%^BOLD%^effect%^RESET%^ - the effect of the philosphy
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/philosophies.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a philosphy into the current list of philosphies.
.EP

.SH Example 1
.SI 5
add_philosophy("theology", "faith", 50, "the power of your faith",
               "/std/effects/religious/theological_debate");
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_philosophy(), query_philosophy_names(), remove_philosophy()

.EP

